---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="About Australian Home Collective and our practical home and lifestyle guides."
>
  <header class="page-intro">
    <div class="narrow">
      <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
      <h1>Practical guidance for Australian homes.</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        Australian Home Collective helps readers compare home and lifestyle choices with clear,
        practical context for Australian households.
      </p>
    </div>
  </header>
  <section class="content narrow">
    <p>
      We write for Australian households, renters, parents, gift-givers and anyone trying to
      make sensible decisions without feeling rushed.
    </p>
    <h2>What we publish</h2>
    <p>
      Our guides explain common product categories, practical trade-offs, local considerations
      and questions worth asking before you decide. We aim to be useful, readable and easy to
      trust.
    </p>
    <p class="small">
      Images and written content on this site are owned by Australian Home Collective unless
      otherwise stated.
    </p>
    <h2>What we avoid</h2>
    <p>
      We do not publish offer-led pages or make unsupported claims about origin,
      sustainability, safety or health benefits. When something needs expert advice, we say
      so plainly.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
